Ever wondered how much working time left until weekend? Have you already done 50% or 80%? Ever wished your week had a progress bar you could watch as it approaches 100%??

Well, now you can have it in your iPhone! Install and watch the progress, instead of actually working :) Customize it and compare to your co-workers.

Your Fridays will never be the same again!

Features:
* beautiful and clear progress bar,
* insightful and funny comments,
* configurable working days and hours,
* free without ads!

